OL,3,CRome brings in E2 tourist charge to
OL,4,Cget close to Trevi fountain
OL,6,FTourists wanting to get close to the
OL,7,FTrevi Fountain will now have to cough
OL,8,Fup two euros (#1.73) to do so, as Rome
OL,9,Fintroduces a new fee structure to
OL,10,Fraise funds and control crowds.
OL,12,FThe first punters to pass the new
OL,13,Fticketing system on Monday seemed
OL,14,Funfazed by the tariff, noting it was a
OL,15,Fsmall price to pay for access to the
OL,16,Fworld-renowned water feature.
OL,18,F"Before, there were problems accessing
OL,19,Fthe fountain. There were a lot of
OL,20,Fpeople. Now, it's very easy," said
OL,21,FIlhan Musbah, a tourist from Morocco.
