OL,6,F"You can take photos, you feel good,
OL,7,Fyou're comfortable, and on top of
OL,8,Fthat, two euros is not much."
OL,10,FThe fee was rolled out in conjunction
OL,11,Fwith a new five euro (#4.32) tourist
OL,12,Fticket fee for some city museums.
OL,14,FIn both cases, residents of Rome are
OL,15,Fexempt from the fees, and extra
OL,16,Frevenue will actually expand the
OL,17,Fnumber of city-run museums that are
OL,18,Ffree for registered Roman residents.
