OL,3,CRome brings in E2 tourist charge to
OL,4,Cget close to Trevi fountain
OL,6,FIt's all part of Rome's efforts to
OL,7,Fmanage tourist flows, with new
OL,8,Fregulations hoped to improve the
OL,9,Fexperience of visiting the city and
OL,10,Foffset cultural heritage maintenance
OL,11,Fcosts.
OL,13,FOfficials estimate it could net the
OL,14,Fcity E6.5 million (#5.6million) extra
OL,15,Fper year.
