OL,3,CRome brings in E2 tourist charge to
OL,4,Cget close to Trevi fountain
OL,6,FThe city decided to impose the Trevi
OL,7,FFountain fee after seeing positive
OL,8,Fresults from a year-long experiment to
OL,9,Fstagger and limit the number of
OL,10,Fvisitors who can reach the front edge
OL,11,Fof the basin by imposing lines and
OL,12,Fpathways for entrance and exit.
OL,14,F"I think tourists were shocked by the
OL,15,Ffact that the city of Rome is only
OL,16,Fasking for 2 euros for a site of this
OL,17,Flevel," Alessandro Onorato, Rome's
OL,18,Fassessor of tourism, said Monday.
