OL,3,CRome brings in E2 tourist charge to
OL,4,Cget close to Trevi fountain
OL,6,FThe Italian fees still pale in
OL,7,Fcomparison to the 45% price hike that
OL,8,FFrench authorities announced for the
OL,9,FLouvre Museum for most non-EU visitors
OL,10,F- including the UK, US and China -
OL,11,Fjumping from E22 (#19) to E32 (#27).
OL,13,FThe Trevi fee, which can be paid in
OL,14,Fadvance online, enables tourists to
OL,15,Fget close to the fountain during prime-
OL,16,Ftime daylight hours (from 11am on
OL,17,Fweekdays and from 9am on weekends).
