OL,3,CRome brings in E2 tourist charge to
OL,4,Cget close to Trevi fountain
OL,6,FThe view for those admiring the late
OL,7,FBaroque masterpiece from the piazza
OL,8,Fabove remains free, as does being up
OL,9,Fclose after 10pm.
OL,11,FVisitors to the fountain, featured in
OL,12,Fmany a film from Federico Fellini's La
OL,13,FDolce Vita to The Lizzie McGuire
OL,14,FMovie, are said to guarantee a return
OL,15,Fto Rome by tossing a coin over their
OL,16,Fshoulder and making a wish.
